WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.100
I can’t believe what Toko-san said.

00:03.840 --> 00:06.160
Nothing will return to the way it used to be.

00:06.820 --> 00:09.780
I’m disliked.

00:10.820 --> 00:13.100
Toko-san said to keep writing in my diary.

00:14.000 --> 00:16.420
I don’t need a diary.

00:17.360 --> 00:19.520
I don’t have anything to write.

00:20.320 --> 00:23.260
Nothing has changed.

00:24.040 --> 00:26.620
I just go to school everyday as usual.

00:27.120 --> 00:30.340
I’m alone during recess and lunchtime, and no one talks to me.
